OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FThe Israeli government has deported
OL,8,Fhundreds of flotilla activists who
OL,9,Fattempted to reach Gaza and whose
OL,10,Ftreatment by a member of Benjamin
OL,11,FNetanyahu's government sparked
OL,12,Finternational condemnation.
OL,14,FAbout 420 activists departed Israel on
OL,15,Fplanes bound for Turkey, where they
OL,16,Flanded Thursday evening in Istanbul.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
