PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FWearing grey sweatsuits and Arab
OL,8,Fkeffiyehs, they descended stairs to
OL,9,Fthe runway flashing two-fingered
OL,10,Fsalutes and chanting "Free Palestine."
OL,11,FSome appeared to be limping.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Netanyahu said on
OL,14,FWednesday he instructed that the
OL,15,Factivists be deported "as soon as
OL,16,Fpossible," after sharply rebuking
OL,17,FIsrael's national security minister
OL,18,Ffor provocative videos showing the
OL,19,Fminister taunting detained flotilla
OL,20,Factivists who were handcuffed and
OL,21,Fkneeling.
OL,26,@rD@VOUrD@fO]wD@WOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
