CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FNetanyahu said that although Israel
OL,8,Fhas every right to stop "provocative
OL,9,Fflotillas of Hamas terrorist
OL,10,Fsupporters," the way National Security
OL,11,FMinister Itamar Ben-Gvir dealt with
OL,12,Fthe activists was "not in line with
OL,13,FIsrael's values and norms."
OL,26,@pD@YOUrD@LO]tD@SOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
