OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FBen-Gvir released videos on Wednesday
OL,8,Fshowing him walking among some of the
OL,9,Fdetainees. In one, activists with
OL,10,Ftheir hands tied behind their backs
OL,11,Fare kneeling, their heads touching the
OL,12,Ffloor inside what appears to be a
OL,13,Fmakeshift detention area on the deck
OL,14,Fof a ship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
