OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FSeveral countries, including Britain,
OL,8,FFrance and Portugal, summoned Israeli
OL,9,Fenvoys on Thursday over concerns about
OL,10,Fthe treatment of flotilla activists,
OL,11,Fmany of whom were citizens of their
OL,12,Fown countries, in protest of Ben-
OL,13,FGvir's actions.
OL,15,FUK Foreign Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,16,Fsaid she was "truly appalled" by the
OL,17,Ffootage saying "this violates the most
OL,18,Fbasic standards of respect and dignity
OL,19,Fin the way people should be treated".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
