OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FTurkey, Greece, Italy and Indonesia
OL,8,Falso condemned Israel for Ben-Gvir's
OL,9,Fcomments and the treatment of flotilla
OL,10,Factivists.
OL,12,FTwo Italian citizens who had been
OL,13,Fdetained by Israel returned home on
OL,14,FThursday, said they had been beaten
OL,15,Fand mistreated, allegations that were
OL,16,Fdenied by Israeli prison officials.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
