PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FDario Carotenuto, an Italian lawmaker,
OL,8,Fsaid he experienced the "longest
OL,9,Fseconds" of his life when Israeli
OL,10,Fforces pointed rifles at activists
OL,11,Finside a detention facility.
OL,13,F"They kicked me in the legs and
OL,14,Fpunched me in the face," said
OL,15,FAlessandro Mantovani, an Italian
OL,16,Fnewspaper journalist.
OL,18,FThe allegations were "false and
OL,19,Fentirely without factual basis," said
OL,20,FZivan Freidin, a spokesperson for the
OL,21,FIsraeli Prison Service.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@HO]uD@AOUvD@XO]zD@VOU{D@`O]
