OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FDozens of the activists' boats began
OL,8,Fsetting sail from Spain to Gaza in
OL,9,FApril. Israel stopped 20 vessels from
OL,10,Fthe group on April 30 near the
OL,11,Fsouthern Greek island of Crete and
OL,12,Fforced most of its activists to
OL,13,Fdisembark.
OL,15,FIsrael took two high-profile
OL,16,Factivists, Spanish-Swedish citizen
OL,17,FSaif Abukeshek and Brazilian citizen
OL,18,FThiago Avila, back to Israel, where
OL,19,Fthey were interrogated and detained
OL,20,Ffor around a week before being
OL,21,Fdeported.
OL,26,@zD@Hr`
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
