OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FThe activists accused Israel of
OL,8,Ftorture, claims Israel denies. Brazil
OL,9,Fand Spain condemned Israel for
OL,10,F"kidnapping" their citizens.
OL,12,FParticipants then regrouped and more
OL,13,Fthan 50 boats departed from the
OL,14,FTurkish port of Marmaris on May 14.
OL,15,FIsraeli forces began stopping the
OL,16,Fboats about 167 miles from the Gaza
OL,17,Fcoastline, according to the flotilla's
OL,18,Fwebsite.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
