PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FIsrael's Foreign Ministry has called
OL,8,Fthe flotilla "a PR stunt at the
OL,9,Fservice of Hamas." The boats carry a
OL,10,Ftiny, symbolic amount of aid.
OL,12,FLast year, Israeli authorities blocked
OL,13,Fa similar attempt involving some 500
OL,14,Factivists.
OL,16,FIsrael has maintained a sea blockade
OL,17,Fof Gaza since Hamas took control of
OL,18,Fthe territory in 2007.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
