PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779466274
OL,3,CIsrael deports hundreds of Gaza
OL,4,Cflotilla activists after global
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FIsraeli authorities intensified it
OL,8,Fafter the Hamas-led militant attacks
OL,9,Fon southern Israel that killed around
OL,10,F1,200 people and saw more than 250
OL,11,Ftaken hostage on October 7, 2023.
OL,13,FCritics say the blockade amounts to
OL,14,Fcollective punishment. Israel says
OL,15,Fit's intended to prevent Hamas from
OL,16,Farming itself.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
